    "&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;In the absence of a detailed noise report including any necessary mitigation measures, the Local Planning Authority are unable to make a full assessment of the impacts of the Air Conditioning Unit on the residential amenities of adjoining neighbours with regard to noise and disturbance, contrary to Policy D3.D(7) and D3.D(9) and D14 of The London Plan 2021 and Policy DM1 of the Harrow Development Management Policies Local Plan (2013).&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;",
    "Due to its prominent positioning in a highly visible location, and its inappropriate and incongruous design the air-conditioning unit first floor rear elevation fronting Vellacott Road, would have an adverse visual impact on the character and appearance of the host building and the wider streetscene, contrary to the high quality design aspirations of the National Planning Policy Framework (2023), Policy D3 (D(1) and D(11)) of The London Plan (2021), Core Policy CS1 (B) of the Harrow Core Strategy (2012) and&nbsp;policy DM 1 of the Harrow Development Management Policies Local Plan (2013)."
